#, c-format
msgid "      Mark the whole issue invalid.\n"
msgstr "      issue 全体を invalid にします。\n"

#: src/issue.c:1140
#, c-format
msgid ""
"      Put the issue on hold using a reviewer-supplied condition instead.\n"
msgstr ""
"      reviewer が指定した condition を使って issue を hold にします。\n"

#: src/issue.c:1138
#, c-format
msgid ""
"      Put the issue on hold using the requested condition if one is active.\n"
msgstr ""
"      requested condition が active の場合はそれを使って issue を hold にしま"
"す。\n"

